<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الْعمرَة وَكَذَا الْحَج<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>ان كَانَ الْجِمَاع فِيهِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قبل التَّحَلُّل الأول<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَإِمَّا الْجِمَاع بعد التَّحَلُّل الأول فَلَا يفْسد بِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
